title: SPECIAL PREVIEW: Up On Game - Hour 1 - CFP Semi-Finals Reaction
itunes:title: SPECIAL PREVIEW: Up On Game - Hour 1 - CFP Semi-Finals Reaction
description:
In hour 1 of Up On Game with LaVar Arrington, T.J. Houshmandzadeh and Plaxico Burress, the guys jump right into the underwhelming CFP semi-final matchups that saw the SEC dominate. Plus, James Jackson from the Straight Facts podcast joins the guys for 'On Ya Head.' Fox Sports Update Anchor Ralph Irving takes the guys down memory lane!
